<subSubSection id="7D0C583D906FE5760ED678541DFD9750" pageId="216" pageNumber="217" type="note">
<paragraph id="2A37B0995001C819BDF1F4754661CAFC" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BF41FC60FD9280D3EF95A848FA41364C" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">The nominotypical subspecies is found along the Gulf Coast of Mexico, as far south as Veracruz, and from Honduras (Erwin and Pearson 2008: 290).</paragraph>
